{"tid":2415971,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"講起異世界動畫，我諗起.......","createTime":"2021-02-20T16:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T18:12:02.000Z","uid":324629,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"84d25de35a684b773744eb62e53ede184772d8a4","tid":2415971,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T16:07:33.000Z","msg":"就係Battle Spirits系列啦！喺咁多套異世界番入面，佢算係一套異類：明明係卡鬥遊戲改編而成嘅漫畫，但係就用Battle Spirits建立左一個世界觀，仲係將battle spirits融入異世界冒險嘅元素，每次睇每一集角色點樣運用卡牌同技巧去對戰真係好刺激<br />\n<br />\n雖然話好多歷代BS動畫都係子供向獨立動畫，但係就係馬神彈（彈爺）系列（Battle Spirits少年激霸，Battle Spirits Saga Brave同埋Battle Spirits 赫盟的加雷特）特別好睇。佢唔止係講成班主角團用BS一路打怪升級嘅公路片劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，更加加入左好多好有深度嘅反思，例如話種族之間嘅仇恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，和理非VS激進武力，去到Battle Spirits brave最後睇住彈爺變成扳機消失真係好催淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />btw彈爺對戰異界王嗰陣嗰句「我就係鍾意佢天下無敵！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋「用生命值硬接！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有成日犧牲劍翼飛龍借core嘅橋段真係好經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw最近2019年製作組特登出左3集嘅saga brave賣情懷之餘繼續超展開新嘅劇情（今次劇情仲涉及穿越時空添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）然後接住就係Battle Spirits赫盟的加雷特動畫（同彈爺系列屬同一時間線）。雖然只係得5集嘅mini series,而且係月更動畫，但係睇內容都係幾高質，有興趣嘅可以追下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只要係以彈爺嘅時空為背景，BS動畫一定好睇，仲可以再戰10年添<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FSt4mpnttqI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFSt4mpnttqI&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbksF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=a24f5076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FSt4mpnttqI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yeEzFhiyU7A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyeEzFhiyU7A&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbksF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=7bbe0115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yeEzFhiyU7A</a><br />\np.s.原來歷代嘅紅紫屬性core光主都係CP wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc50ad94a0f8cfff23b7edbe4f1bc717086909f","tid":2415971,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T16:07:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5feeeda0e05e0d38215244f0a8e55af4530b0d0e","tid":2415971,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T16:08:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8784d1622ff0deaf10a0e39bc092df094c0b7737","tid":2415971,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T16:08:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6405dc41578d1868ff96d0803f4a9eb23c18b2a","tid":2415971,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T16:08:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f740bc050a4e84916f0e778b33dbabedfc1d47a","tid":2415971,"uid":198822,"